Hey there everyone,<p>We recently launched Posterity Automations[1] as a way to trigger tasks in the event of death and if  we can manually verify it.<p>We&#x27;re trying to prioritize partnerships and integrations that people care the about, roughly around two important end goals:<p><pre><code>  1. Expedite access to any funds or financial accounts by your loved ones;
  2. Protect privacy, by deleting or transferring accounts to the person of your choice.
</code></pre>
Curious if there are any services you use that you feel like should have a legacy management options, but currently don’t.<p>If you’re the operator of a service for consumers or small businesses, we’d love to hear from you as well, as we’re thinking about offering a simple API to handle it end-to-end.<p>[1] &lt;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;posterity.life&#x2F;automations&gt;
